O<\/span><\/span><span class=\"EOP SCXW39453840 BCX0\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">4 janvier 2023 &#8211; Brice Castaing <br> <span class=\"update_date\">Date de mise \u00e0 jour : 23 avril 2024<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><ul class=\"post_tags\"><li  style=\"background-color: rgba(29, 99, 239, .1); color: rgba(29, 99, 239); padding: 0.45rem 1.6rem; border-radius: 25px; margin-right: 8px; font-weight: 500; transition: background-color 300ms ease, color 300ms ease; display: block;\">SEO<\/li><\/ul><\/p>\n<\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_section el_class=&#8221;content-ressource&#8221;][vc_row el_class=&#8221;content-article&#8221;][vc_column]<div class=\"text-bloc liste-puce-bleu\"><p aria-level=\"2\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\" lang=\"FR-FR\" xml:lang=\"FR-FR\" data-contrast=\"auto\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\">La <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\">mani\u00e8re de structurer <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\">un site web et son contenu <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\">a un impact <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\">important<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\"> pour le<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\"> SEO<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\">. <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\">En tant que titres et sous-titres, l<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\">es<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\"> balises <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW244712916 BCX0\">Hn<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\"> sont indispensables pour construire un SEO on-site et une UX de qualit\u00e9 pour votre contenu ! <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\">Ces balises vont <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\">faciliter<\/span> <span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\">pour vos visiteurs <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\">et les moteurs<\/span> <span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\">de recherche <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\">l\u2019identification des <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\">th\u00e9matiques<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\"> abord\u00e9<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\">es<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\"> dans votre page<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW244712916 BCX0\">.<\/span><\/span><span class=\"EOP SCXW244712916 BCX0\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"image-single-wrapper text-center\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/balisagehn.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Balisagehn\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/balisagehn.png 1920w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/balisagehn-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/balisagehn-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/balisagehn-1536x864.png 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row el_class=&#8221;content-article article-table-matiere&#8221;][vc_column]<div class=\"text-bloc toc\"><p class=\"titre_3\">Table des mati\u00e8res<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_74 ez-toc-wrap-center counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"cursor:inherit\">Sommaire<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 eztoc-toggle-hide-by-default' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"#\" data-href=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/ressources\/seo\/balises-hn-referencement-seo\/#Quest-ce_quune_balise_Heading_H_Tag_ou_Hn%E2%80%AF\" >Qu\u2019est-ce qu\u2019une balise Heading, H Tag ou Hn\u202f?\u00a0<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"#\" data-href=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/ressources\/seo\/balises-hn-referencement-seo\/#Comment_utiliser_une_balise_H1%E2%80%AF\" >Comment utiliser une balise H1\u202f?\u00a0<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"#\" data-href=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/ressources\/seo\/balises-hn-referencement-seo\/#Comment_utiliser_les_balises_H2_H3_et_Hn_suivantes%E2%80%AF\" >Comment utiliser les balises H2, H3 et Hn suivantes\u202f?\u00a0<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"#\" data-href=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/ressources\/seo\/balises-hn-referencement-seo\/#Les_erreurs_frequentes_sur_lutilisation_des_balises_Hn\" >Les erreurs fr\u00e9quentes sur l\u2019utilisation des balises Hn\u00a0<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"#\" data-href=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/ressources\/seo\/balises-hn-referencement-seo\/#Comment_evaluer_letat_de_votre_balisage_Hn%E2%80%AF\" >Comment \u00e9valuer l\u2019\u00e9tat de votre balisage Hn\u202f?\u00a0<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row el_class=&#8221;content-article&#8221;][vc_column]<div class=\"text-bloc\"><h2 aria-level=\"2\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Qu\u2019est-ce qu\u2019une balise Heading, H Tag ou Hn\u202f?<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Les balises Hn sont des \u00e9l\u00e9ments HTML utilis\u00e9s pour d\u00e9finir les titres d&#8217;une page.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Les balises peuvent \u00eatre num\u00e9rot\u00e9es de 1 \u00e0 6 selon l\u2019importance et la position du titre ou du sous-titre au sein de la structure globale du document. Elles hi\u00e9rarchisent l\u2019information et facilitent la lecture des internautes, comme des crawlers Google. En effet, lire la table des mati\u00e8res avec tous les Hn permet de comprendre rapidement o\u00f9 sont les informations cl\u00e9s, les arguments et les passages qui nous int\u00e9ressent, en tant que lecteur.\u00a0<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">A noter<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">\u202f: Ne pas confondre le codage des balises Hn qui se pr\u00e9sente ainsi\u202f: &lt;h1&gt;\u2026&lt;\/h1&gt;\u202f; &lt;h2&gt;\u2026&lt;\/h2&gt; \u2026 etc. avec le codage de l\u2019ent\u00eate de la page qui s\u2019\u00e9crit de cette fa\u00e7on\u202f: &lt;head&gt;\u2026&lt;\/head&gt;<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 aria-level=\"2\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Comment utiliser une balise H1\u202f?<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">La balise H1 s\u2019utilise sur le titre principal d\u2019une page.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Son contenu devrait toujours \u00eatre repr\u00e9sentatif du contenu g\u00e9n\u00e9ral de la page. Un bon titre H1 doit \u00eatre engageant, donner envie de lire le contenu de la page, et, pour votre SEO, inclure l\u2019expression principale vis\u00e9e dans votre strat\u00e9gie d\u2019acquisition.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Il est recommand\u00e9\u202f:<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:765,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">de n\u2019inclure qu\u2019un seul H1 par page\u202f;<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:765,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">d\u2019avoir un H1 unique, c\u2019est-\u00e0-dire ne pas avoir plusieurs pages avec le m\u00eame H1\u202f;<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:765,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">d\u2019avoir un H1 qui soit diff\u00e9rent de votre balise TITLE\u202f;<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:765,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">d\u2019\u00e9viter d\u2019\u00e9crire un titre trop long, il n\u2019y a pas de r\u00e8gle officielle mais nous recommandons d\u2019\u00e9crire moins de 70 caract\u00e8res et d\u2019inclure l\u2019expression SEO vis\u00e9e plut\u00f4t en d\u00e9but de balise\u202f;<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"1\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:765,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">de configurer un CSS afin que la balise H1 s\u2019affiche de fa\u00e7on plus grande (taille de la police d\u2019\u00e9criture) que les autres Hn.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Par exemple, pour cet article, selon notre angle d\u2019\u00e9criture, nous aurions pu choisir un autre H1 marquant tel que \u201cStructurer ses articles de blog avec des balises Hn\u201d ou \u201cBalise HN : d\u00e9finition et usages\u201d, etc.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"text-bloc\"><h2 aria-level=\"2\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Comment utiliser les balises H2, H3 et Hn suivantes\u202f?<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Tout comme pour le titre principal H1 de la page, les balises Hn suivantes ont leur importance. Les H tags (et non hashtag, c\u2019est pas la m\u00eame chose\u202f:D ) du H2 au H6 sont destin\u00e9s \u00e0 faciliter l\u2019identification des chapitres ou des sous-th\u00e8mes abord\u00e9s.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><strong>Voici nos conseils pour les Hn :\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Leur contenu devrait inclure des termes strat\u00e9giques (synonymes ou connexes au terme principal)\u202f;<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li data-leveltext=\"\uf0b7\" data-font=\"Symbol\" data-listid=\"2\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;\uf0b7&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria