eb.\u00a0<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">N\u2019oubliez pas, le balisage des headings ne doit pas servir pour embellir vos pages. On ne l\u2019utilise pas pour mettre des bouts de contenu en grand, mais bien pour structurer les id\u00e9es dans votre texte. Si vous souhaitez mettre en avant des phrases au sein de votre contenu, utilisez plut\u00f4t des class CSS (le gras, l\u2019italique) ou une ponctuation bien amen\u00e9e ! Rythmez vos phrases, a\u00e9rez vos textes&#8230; et faites-vous relire au besoin.\u00a0<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 aria-level=\"2\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Comment \u00e9valuer l\u2019\u00e9tat de votre balisage Hn\u202f?<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:40,&quot;335559739&quot;:0,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Afin d\u2019analyser les Headings d\u2019une page, vous pourrez utiliser des outils gratuits (extensions de navigateur d\u00e9di\u00e9es au SEO) ou faire une recherche directe dans le code source.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Voici ce qu\u2019une extension de ce type remonte par exemple pour la page <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/ressources\/seo\/content-pruning-suppression-contenu\/\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/ressources\/seo\/content-pruning-suppression-contenu\/<\/span><i><\/i><\/a><span data-contrast=\"auto\"> \u202fqui est dans les tops r\u00e9sultats de Google sur la recherche \u00ab<\/span><i><span data-contrast=\"auto\">\u202fcontent pruning\u202f<\/span><\/i><span data-contrast=\"auto\">\u00bb :<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"image-single-wrapper text-center\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"621\" height=\"372\" src=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/structure-hn-article-content-pruning.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"structure-hn-article-content-pruning\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/structure-hn-article-content-pruning.jpg 621w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/structure-hn-article-content-pruning-300x180.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 621px) 100vw, 621px\" \/><\/div><div class=\"text-bloc\"><p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">On peut visualiser directement les \u00e9l\u00e9ments suivants\u202f:<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li data-leveltext=\"-\" data-font=\"Calibri\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335551671&quot;:0,&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;-&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"0\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Le H1 est bien la 1<\/span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">\u00e8re<\/span><span data-contrast=\"auto\"> balise de la page\u202f;<\/span><\/li>\n<li data-leveltext=\"-\" data-font=\"Calibri\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335551671&quot;:0,&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;-&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&