ot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;-&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"0\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Des termes connexes \u00e0 l\u2019expression principale sont inclus dans les balises Hn\u202f: \u00ab\u202fsuppression de contenus\u202f\u00bb, \u00ab\u202fsupprimer du contenu\u202f\u00bb, \u00ab\u202fcontenus \u00e0 supprimer\u202f\u00bb et \u00ab\u202fsuppression d\u2019une page\u202f\u00bb\u202f;<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li data-leveltext=\"-\" data-font=\"Calibri\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335551671&quot;:0,&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;-&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"0\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">L\u2019ordre des Hn est respect\u00e9\u202f;<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li data-leveltext=\"-\" data-font=\"Calibri\" data-listid=\"3\" data-list-defn-props=\"{&quot;335551671&quot;:0,&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;-&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"0\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Aucun Hn de structure (menu, footer..) n\u2019est pr\u00e9sent sur la page.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Lorsqu\u2019une analyse du balisage d\u2019un site complet est n\u00e9cessaire, il est pr\u00e9f\u00e9rable d\u2019utiliser un crawler. Ce logiciel permettra d\u2019extraire des donn\u00e9es utiles \u00e0 cette analyse.\u00a0<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Le crawler <\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Screaming Frog<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">, dans sa version payante, permet notamment de faire cette analyse. Il permettra, une fois configur\u00e9, de donner le nombre de H1, H2, H3, H4\u2026\u00a0 par page. Vous pourrez \u00e9galement extraire le contenu de ces balises afin d\u2019auditer la s\u00e9mantique utilis\u00e9e. Ce crawl vous permettra de d\u00e9tecter les soucis d\u2019absence (ou de manque de titres) ou d\u2019identifier les duplications de contenus qui peuvent \u00eatre pr\u00e9sents sur plusieurs pages.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Un r\u00e9f\u00e9renceur SEO est un sp\u00e9cialiste du r\u00e9f\u00e9rencement naturel. Il vous aidera \u00e0 identifier les forces de votre site et \u00e0 optimiser chacune de vos pages pour attirer toujours plus d\u2019internautes. Si vous souhaitez l\u2019accompagnement personnalis\u00e9 d\u2019un r\u00e9f\u00e9renceur SEO, <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/contact\/\">contactez NOIISE<i><\/i><\/a><\/strong>. Notre \u00e9quipe sera heureuse de vous aider dans votre d\u00e9marche d\u2019optimisation SEO.<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][v